Title: S27:E3 - Helping You Build Machine Learning Products (Pau Labarta Bajo)
Description: Meet Pau Bajo, Machine Learning Engineer and Educator at Real-World Machine Learning. Pau talks to Saron about transitioning from working daily in Excel to Python, why data is everything, and what skills early developers need to foster if they want a career in machine learning.
